Volume: 12
Issue: 1
Keyword: POOLING, STOCK KEEPING UNIT, SKU, RATIONALIZATION, PRODUCT VARIETY, INVENTORY MANAGEMENT, SUBOPTIMAL INVENTORY POLICY
