Title: Green Service: Construct Development and Measurement Validation
Author-Name: Chan, Ting‐Yan
Author-Name: Wong, Christina W. Y.
Author-Name: Lai, Kee‐Hung
Author-Name: Lun, Venus Y. H.
Author-Name: Ng, Chi To
